    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir wiſſus winnu Pilſ-\nfahns/ ar winnu Mahju-Wee-\ntahn/ un ar wiſſahin winnu Pil-\nlim fadedſinaja tee ar Ugguni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un rehne wiſſu Laupiju-\nmu/ un wiſſu/ ko tee bij ſagnhſt-\njufchi/ no Zilwekeim un Lohpeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un atneffe to pee Mohsus kas tahdu Zilweſtu nokawis irr/\nun Eeleasara ta Preestera/ un pee un ikweens/ kas tahdu nokantu\nwiſſas Israëta Behrnu Drau- aiſkahrıs irr : juhs buhs treſcha\ndses/ tohs Zeetumneekus/ un tohs Deenaâ/ un ſeptitâ Deenâ ſchkih-\nSubstitus / un to Lampijumu/ stitees/ ir juhs/ ir juhſeim Sa-\nus to Lehgert Dioaba Klajumôs/ guhſtiteem.\nkas pee Jardanas prett Jeriku irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Mohsus un Eelea-\nfars tas Preesteris / un wiſſi\nDraudses Wirfneeki gahje win-\nneem pretti / ahra preeſsch Lehg-\ngera.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Mohsus apſaittaſs\nprett teem Karra-Wirfneekem/\nteem Wirfneekem pahr tubêsto-\nkheemi/un teemWirfneekem pahr\nſimteem/ kas no tahs Karra Rau-\nſchanas nahze.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Mohsus ſazztja uſ\nteem: Effat juhs tad wiſſas See-\nwas likkuſcht dſihwoht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rangi / ſchahs bija / kas\ntohs Israëta Behrnus zaar Bi-\nleama Padohmu darrija pahr-\nkahpt prett to KUNGU/ ta Peo-\nra deht / kadeht ta Mohziba tap-\npe ſtarp ta KUNGA Drau-\ndses.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nu tad nokaujeet wiſſus/\nkas no Wihra-Kahrtas irr starp-\nteem Behrmineem / un nokaujeet\nwiſſas Seewas / kas Wihrn irr\natsinnuſchas un pee Wihra gul-\nlejuſchas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tomehr wiſſus Behrnt-\nnus no Seewu-Kahrtas/ kas pee\nne tahda Wihra guliejuſchas irr/\npametteet dſihwus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un juhs paleezeet ahram\nLehgexa ſeptin Deenas/ ikweens/\nkas tahdu Zilweſtu nokawis irr/\nun ikweens/ kas tahdu nokantu\naiſkahrıs irr : juhs buhs treſcha\ndeenaâ/ un ſeptitâ Deenâ ſchkih-\nstitees/ ir juhs/ ir juhſeim Sa-\nguhſtiteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un juhs buhs wiſſas\nDrehbes/ un wiſſu/ kas no Ah-\ndahm taiſihts/ un wiſſu/ kas no\nKasit- (Spalwahm) darrihts /\nun wiſſus Kohku Nihkus ſchkih-\nſticht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Eeleasars tas Preeste-\nrıs ſazzija us wiſſeem Karra-\nWiheem/ kas Karra gahjuſchi\nbija : Schis irr tahs Bauflibas\nLikums/ ko tas KUNGS Moh-\nſum irr pawehſteis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "To Seltn tikai / un to\nGudrabu/ un to Warn/ un to\nDselsu/ un to Alwu/ un Swinnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jekatru Leetu/ kas Uggu-\nni zeesch / buhs juhs liſt zaar\nUggunt eet/ ka ta ſchkihſta tohp/\nun tafchu buhs tam ar Glazzi-\nſchanas Uhdeni ſchkihſtitam tapt/\nbet wiſſ/ kas Ugguni ne zeesch/ to\nbuhs juhs liſt zaar Uhdeni eet,\n"
    }
  ],
